precis:
Amendment to the ARCTIC SHIPPING POLLUTION PREVENTION REGULATIONS extending
the operating season in Artic Shipping Safety Control Zone I, permitting
Canarctic Shipping Company Limited to make additional voyages to and from
the Bent Horn oil terminal on Cameron Island.
